Class Presenter

java.lang.Object
presenter.Presenter
All Implemented Interfaces:
ActionListener, EventListener, IPresenter
public class Presenter extends Object implements ActionListener, IPresenter
This class represents the Presenter, which is in charge of the communication between the model and the view.
